Quay tàu lại!

332
00:45:52,072 --> 00:45:53,282
Quay...

333
00:45:55,322 --> 00:45:56,992
- Bình tĩnh, anh bạn.
- Quay tàu lại!

334
00:45:57,072 --> 00:45:57,912
Khoan đã!

335
00:45:58,032 --> 00:45:59,452
Bình tĩnh, anh bạn.

336
00:46:01,582 --> 00:46:02,412
George?

337
00:46:02,952 --> 00:46:03,962
George!

338
00:46:06,882 --> 00:46:07,792
